        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/develleoper/{size}/19220_2.png",
        "created_at": "2022-01-26T22:09:07.434Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I‚Äôd like to add that many of the signal emoji are nearly illegible on windows and are an accessibility issue. Most operating systems provide emoji which best suit their screen resolutions, color-contrast, and pixel densities, and Signal should allow the option to respect them.</p>",
