        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/joejoetv/{size}/54723_2.png",
        "created_at": "2025-11-17T19:31:42.029Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I would also really like to see this feature. Even just selecting from a few Emoji sets would be totally fine for me, like e.g. The Telegram desktop client does where you can select between Apple, Google‚Äôs Emoji, Twemoji and JoyPixel. Supporting the default font on e.g. Linux would be even better, but I can see this being more difficult.</p>\n<p>Since there hasn‚Äôt been any action for some time here, I hope this is still being considered.</p>",
